# Xtream IPTV Player - Environment Configuration
# =============================================
#
# The app calls your Xtream server DIRECTLY from the browser.
# Your Xtream server MUST have CORS headers enabled for this to work.
#
# To enable CORS on your Xtream server (admin panel):
#   - Go to Settings -> API/CORS
#   - Add your app's origin to allowed origins
#   - Example for local dev: http://localhost:5173
#   - Or use * to allow all origins
#
# No VITE_XTREAM_PROXY_TARGET is needed anymore —
# the server URL comes from your login form, not this file.